{"id":109650,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/書展第一回/","date":"2010-09-29T08:32:06Z","modified":"2010-09-29T08:32:06Z","title":"書展第一回","content":"<p><p align=\"right\">葉一知</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>今天去了書展逛了個圈, 第一日好好行, 人又少. 買了以下幾本書:</p>\n<p>專治政無能之起你個錨 (毛小璐, haha, 諗下佢個英文名)(大眾書局有售)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754930-Cover_act.jpg\"><img alt=\"Picture\" border=\"0\" height=\"512\" hspace=\"5\" src=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754930-Cover_act.jpg&#038;mode=medium\" vspace=\"5\" width=\"360\" /></a> </p>\n<p>據說次文化堂十年來第一次唔出政治漫畫, 但一雞死一雞鳴, 呢本政治笑話很爆笑.其中一篇非常正, 忍唔住scan出來share, 用來說功能組別固然可以, 用來講近日的大浪西灣事件, 我覺得都好啱feel:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754933-what%20is%20politics.jpg\"><img alt=\"Picture\" border=\"0\" height=\"392\" hspace=\"5\" src=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754933-what%20is%20politics.jpg&#038;mode=medium\" vspace=\"5\" width=\"514\" /></a></p>\n<p>(按圖放大) </p>\n<p> 呢本書仲係用廣東話寫, 好悍衛粵語啊!</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>地產霸權 (潘慧嫻) (天地,天窗等都有售)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754932-Property%20Hegemony.jpg\"><img alt=\"Picture\" border=\"0\" height=\"414\" hspace=\"5\" src=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754932-Property%20Hegemony.jpg&#038;mode=medium\" vspace=\"5\" width=\"331\" /></a> </p>\n<p>今年話題作, 揭露香港的地產勢力. 很值得參考, 煲左呢本書, 以後再看香港現狀, 會有更全面的角度.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>香港大靈異 &#8211; 神異傳說及民間信仰 (陳雲) (天地有售) </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754931-Hong%20Kong%20Myth.jpg\"><img alt=\"Picture\" border=\"0\" height=\"465\" hspace=\"5\" src=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/resserver.php?blogId=11138&#038;resource=2754931-Hong%20Kong%20Myth.jpg&#038;mode=medium\" vspace=\"5\" width=\"331\" /></a> </p>\n<p>近年常看陳雲, 去年的&#8221;難忘香港食與色&#8221;, 我覺得非常好看, 今次講靈異, 好地道, 古靈精怪, 也很合我口味啊.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>過兩日再去, 睇下再掃啲咩先. </p>\n<p>賣多次廣告: 大家記住去大眾書局看看<a href=\"http://diumanpark.mysinablog.com/index.php?op=ViewArticle&#038;articleId=2436904\">中女起錨</a>呀. </p>\n<p> </p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}